files.licenseComments:
The information in the file is:

This is based on SHA256 implementation in LibTomCrypt that was released into public domain by Tom St Denis.

We checked the internet link https://www.libtom.net/LibTomCrypt/, the following text was displayed:

LibTomCrypt is free for all purposes under the public domain. This includes commercial use, redistribution and even branching.

Thus, we concluded public domain.
The information was retrieved on June 8th, 2024.
